name: Chitubox Sliced 3D Model
summary: A CBDDLP is a sliced 3D model created by Chitubox, a program used to prepare 3D models for 3D printing. Using a CBDDLP file, various 3D printers can print the object the file describes. From within Chitubox, users can save 3D models as CBDDLP files and transfer the files to connected 3D printers.
